    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2017 Focus RS is a prime example of hot-hatch engineering, featuring the 2.3L EcoBoost inline-four equipped with a twin-scroll turbocharger. The highlight is the Ford Performance AWD system with Dynamic Torque Vectoring, which manages yaw control and provides immense grip through the apex. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission with a short-throw shifter. The suspension utilizes dual-mode adjustable dampers, providing excellent chassis composure. It remains mechanically sound with consistent boost pressure and firm pedal feel from the Brembo four-piston front calipers. While showing minor aesthetic patina from road use, the drivetrain and structural integrity are uncompromising.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
