    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my car, and honestly, it's been such a fantastic ride. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It's got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and driving great. If you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for many more miles of memories, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
