    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six. This powerplant utilizes a sequential forced induction system that delivers a smooth, broad torque curve, paired with the highly sought-after Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox. The drivetrain is rounded out by a factory helical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. The suspension maintains its original double-wishbone geometry, providing excellent lateral grip and communicative feedback. Mechanically, the vehicle is robust; the engine holds steady oil pressure, and the turbochargers spool cleanly without shaft play or smoke. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and fresh synchromesh fluid in the transmission. This is a high-performance example suited for the purist who prioritizes mechanical synchronization and analog engagement.",
